<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_mim.connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship">
<p>
A <b>connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> and  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> that implements the
ARM concept of <express_ref linkend="Bare_die:arm:Bare_die_arm.Connection_zone_bare_die_interface_plane_relationship"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_mim.connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.wr:WR1">
A <b>connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship</b> shall not be any other type of  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> or any other type of  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_mim.connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.wr:WR2">
A <b>connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship</b> shall relate to a  <express_ref linkend="Non_feature_shape_element:mim:Non_feature_shape_element_mim.seating_plane"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.WR3
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_mim.connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.wr:WR3">
A <b>connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship</b> shall relate to a  <express_ref linkend="Non_feature_shape_element:mim:Non_feature_shape_element_mim.seating_plane"/>, with a name of 'plane'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.WR4
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_mim.connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.wr:WR4">
A <b>connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship</b> shall relate to a  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> with a description of 'connection zone'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.WR5
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_mim.connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.wr:WR5">
A <b>connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship</b> shall have a description of 'area' or 'edge'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.WR6
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_mim.connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.wr:WR6">
A <b>connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship</b> shall have the same <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect.of_shape"/> through the  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> supertype and through the <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.related_shape_aspect"/> in the  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> supertype. 
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.WR7
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_mim.connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.wr:WR7">
A <b>connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship</b> shall have the same <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect.of_shape"/> through the  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> supertype and through the <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.relating_shape_aspect"/> in the  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> supertype. 
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.WR8
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_mim.connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.wr:WR8">
A <b>connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship</b> shall be related to one  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> with a description of 'connection zone' as the 'derived zone'. 
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
UR: connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.UR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_mim.connection_zone_interface_plane_relationship.ur:UR1">
The name shall be unique.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: connection_zone_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_mim.connection_zone_constraint">
The <b>connection_zone_constraint</b> rule constrains the use of
<express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> and <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/> when implementing the ARM concepts
of <express_ref linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone:arm:Feature_and_connection_zone_arm.Connection_zone"/> and the associated colour.
</ext_description>

<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_mim.connection_zone_constraint.wr:WR1">
Each instance of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> with a description of 'connection zone'
shall be referenced at least once.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Feature_and_connection_zone_mim.connection_zone_constraint.wr:WR2">
Each instance of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> with a description of 'connection zone'
shall be referenced by at least one <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> with a 
name of 
'connection',
'minimum attachment region size',
'maximum attachment region size',
'external connection area',
'external connection zone',
'internal connection zone',
'mounting area', or
'terminal connection zone'.
</ext_description>

</ext_descriptions>
